            array('id' => '11','key' => 'footer-section','value' => '{"contact":{"language":{"en":{"contact_desc":"DoctorHub is your all-in-one healthcare management solution, designed to simplify how patients, hospitals, and healthcare providers connect. From doctor appointments and investigations to home services and secure payments \\u2014 manage everything in one place with ease and confidence.\\r\\n\\u00a9 2025 DoctorHub. All Rights Reserved."},"fr":{"contact_desc":"\\"DoctorHub est votre solution tout-en-un de gestion des soins de sant\\u00e9, con\\u00e7ue pour simplifier la connexion entre les patients, les h\\u00f4pitaux et les prestataires de soins de sant\\u00e9. Des rendez-vous chez le m\\u00e9decin aux investigations en passant par les services \\u00e0 domicile et les paiements s\\u00e9curis\\u00e9s, g\\u00e9rez tout au m\\u00eame endroit en toute simplicit\\u00e9 et en toute confiance.\\r\\n\\u00a9 2025 DocteurHub. Tous droits r\\u00e9serv\\u00e9s.\\""},"es":{"contact_desc":"\\"DoctorHub es su soluci\\u00f3n de gesti\\u00f3n de atenci\\u00f3n m\\u00e9dica todo en uno, dise\\u00f1ada para simplificar la forma en que se conectan los pacientes, los hospitales y los proveedores de atenci\\u00f3n m\\u00e9dica. Desde citas m\\u00e9dicas e investigaciones hasta servicios a domicilio y pagos seguros: administre todo en un solo lugar con facilidad y confianza.\\r\\n\\u00a9 2025 DoctorHub. Reservados todos los derechos.\\""},"ar":{"contact_desc":"\\"DoctorHub \\u0647\\u0648 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0634\\u0627\\u0645\\u0644 \\u0644\\u0625\\u062f\\u0627\\u0631\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0631\\u0639\\u0627\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0635\\u062d\\u064a\\u0629\\u060c \\u0648\\u0647\\u0648 \\u0645\\u0635\\u0645\\u0645 \\u0644\\u062a\\u0628\\u0633\\u064a\\u0637 \\u0643\\u064a\\u0641\\u064a\\u0629 \\u062a\\u0648\\u0627\\u0635\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0631\\u0636\\u0649 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u0634\\u0641\\u064a\\u0627\\u0